channel.title: Error Loading... Please Contact Staff! On Webclient[Semi-Resolved]
channel.description: Okay, so I just made a custom webclient for my server. I have my client jarred and signed, I have both, my client.jar and cache uploaded to Dropbox in the public folder, and my CacheDownloader class was set to the correct link to my cache. However, if you do not already have the cache installed, when you go to my webclient, it gives you the "Error Loading... Please Contact Staff!" error... Can anybody help me please? This person is having the same problem, but I think he may have explained the issue better. Take a look at his post. http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php?topic=479229.0
